      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t关于地雷，<br/>\n<br/>\n１９９７年发起的渥太华公约，禁止使用地雷，<br/>\n<br/>\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ottawa_Treaty<br/>\n<br/>\n但是，<br/>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>By 2022, 164 states had signed the treaty.[3] One state (the Marshall Islands) has signed but not ratified the treaty, while <b>32 UN states, including China, Russia, and the United States have not; making a total of 33 United Nations states not party</b>.[4][5]</blockquote><br/>\n<br/>\n鹅跌和孝子都没有签，<br/>\n<br/>\n美国也没签，估计是看前面俩货没签不敢签，签了就是自毁长城，\t\t</div>",
